public abstract class StudyController<C extends StudyCommand>
extends AutomaticSaveAjaxableFormController<C,Study,StudyDao>

Base Controller class to handle the basic work flow in the Creation / Updation of a Study Design This uses AbstractTabbedFlowFormController to implement tabbed workflow
